    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Deo Soli <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Invict</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> Myt<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>rae</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Iul</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Macrinus <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>immun</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>VIII <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> ex voto <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>suscept</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> solvit <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Altar war in mehrere Fragmente gebrochen. An den Vorderseiten der pulvini Stierköpfe, dazwischen Kopf des Sol; auf der linken Nebenseite urceus und patera, auf der rechten Beil und Messerfutteral.</p>
            </div>
